description: Greek yoghurt makes this healthier wholemeal muffins super moist and fluffy.
name: Wholemeal Blueberry & Yoghurt Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Stir in the blueberries, reserving a small handful. Scoop the batter into the muffin cases, top each muffin with blueberries and bake for 1820 minutes until golden. Cool for 10 minutes on a wire rack and serve.
